{"tid":2347686,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"居民嬲爆 「搞到咁政府好無能」","createTime":"2020-12-31T08:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T08:35:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ac7a4ae46d0722856a5a2cf990a68a4e5ff6bbad","tid":2347686,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:35:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/ZELZI7CYGRFF5EJ4BGWLIC7D7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FZELZI7CYGRFF5EJ4BGWLIC7D7Q%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmyF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=1967be63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FZELZI7CYGRFF5EJ4BGWLIC7D7Q%2F&h=ec8e2d10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/ZELZI7CYGRFF5EJ4BGWLIC7D7Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n居民嬲爆 「搞到咁政府好無能」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8ZCjE_VKuYRieq1w4VKsSP5yHbQ=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4JBWSS5AXVCDHCVHQF35D5WOIA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8ZCjE_VKuYRieq1w4VKsSP5yHbQ%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4JBWSS5AXVCDHCVHQF35D5WOIA.jpg&h=fb0ed8d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■采頤花園有大廈被列入強制檢疫名單。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府一日內向43幢大廈發出強制檢測令，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘆病毒像便利店散佈全港<br />\n<br />\n居住新蒲崗采頤花園第11座低層的梅太昨從記者口中獲知大廈被列為強制檢疫名單，她批評「有啲過份囉，搞到咁覺得政府好無能」。她續斥政府抗疫不力令多區爆發疫情，「上次醫護叫咗佢封關㗎啦，佢又亂咁放啲人入嚟&hellip;&hellip;𠵱家周圍爆啦」。她認為「政府要負好大責任囉.&hellip;&hellip;第三、第四波都無理由搞到咁」。她又不滿政府對社區檢測的資訊並不透明，部份長者未必清楚，最近的社區檢測站距離采頤花園約有15分鐘路程，政府有必要提供流動檢疫站，以便居民檢測。<br />\n<br />\n另一住低層的鄭女士認為若要強制檢測，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n采頤花園第9座居民田太得悉隔離11座需要強制檢測後，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n同屬疫廈的彩雲一邨紫霄樓及繡文樓亦需強制檢測，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n繡文樓居民吳先生坦言。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n紫霄樓居民詹小姐則稱前日已做過檢測並收到陰性結果，。。。。。。。。。。"}]}